replyContent:
Hi, thanks for your stars,
1. You can not make holes, they are made autommatically, 1 hole for every queen you have, but you need 25 workers for each hole, so: 3 holes you need  75 workers. Only for red ants.
2. You can only send spiders to enemy ant nests
3. You can hold a spot, by clicking on an empty space and click on the shield button.

Thanks
